Definition: suitable or at a time that is suitable or advantageous especially for a particular purpose
Example: an opportune place to make camp; an opportune arrival; an opportune time to receive guests
Synonyms: noun, state, opportunity, attribute, opportuneness, INOPPORTUNE, ADVANTAGEOUS, suitable, or, at, a, time, that, is, advantageous, especially, for, particular, purpose, an, opportune, place, to, make, camp, arrival, receive, guests
Category: adj.all
